{"tid":2038124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲開乜花？","createTime":"2020-05-27T11:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T11:13:55.000Z","uid":43549,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2eeb539beef9636752dbf49dc2eb5bb1cf8e880","tid":2038124,"uid":43549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"又吹五區開花，究竟開花仲有咩目的？<br />\n旺角由班狗企，手足快啲走，唔好再撚班狗啦<br />\n今日好多都一朝早就出黎，到而家都12個鐘<br />\n開花仲幫到咩？唔好再浪漫主義或者覺得一定要出下去企下叫下先對得住手足<br />\n而家有600幾個手足比狗咬左，真係想做嘢出力嘅不如去狗屋幫下班家屬好過啦<br />\n買水買食物或者俾櫈遮或者其他必須品支援下佢地會仲實際"},{"pid":"b8bb8d88e5174cbf21331a9546256186c1516a86","tid":2038124,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"係旺角 冇目標係到嗌 等圍捕 建議即走 <br />\n其他區/屋企要人"},{"pid":"804289361d8b4f05aa02f2b46b5edef4964c1b32","tid":2038124,"uid":43549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cc40e888e118c5daf1b5dc759e0928be976fc15","tid":2038124,"uid":43549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}